Flash Briefing Skill

Developer Terms of Use
des:
Follow the latest career opportunities at the City of Tamarac, Florida, within Alexa’s Flash Briefing.

Add the City of Tamarac Careers Hotline to your Flash Briefing and move it to the top of your news by going to Settings in the Alexa app. You can manage your Flash Briefing under Account.

After adding the City of Tamarac Careers Hotline, you can say “Alexa, what’s my Flash Briefing?” or “Alexa, what’s in the news?” to hear the latest.
